        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Form relative clauses with a comma, a relative pronoun matching the noun's class and case, and the conjugated verb at the end: \"Wien ist eine Stadt, die in à–sterreich liegt.\"",
            "Use nominative relative pronouns (der, das, die, die) when the relative pronoun is the subject of the relative clause.",
            "Describe locations using cardinal directions with im + [Richtung] or [Richtung]lich von + dative: \"Wien liegt im Osten von à–sterreich.\""
        ],
